{"tid":1135018,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國防大臣韋廉信遭撤職 涉華為洩密事件","createTime":"2019-05-02T05:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T05:18:35.000Z","uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"50c71399aa886b6cb21f528bce7ad167f15f3a07","tid":1135018,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:03:56.000Z","msg":"英國政府徹查國家安全委員會有關華為洩密事件有新進展，首相文翠珊決定撤除國防大臣韋廉信(Gavin Williamson)職務。<br />\n<br />\n首相府周三發表聲明，表示文翠珊的決定是針對韋廉信未經授權洩露國家安全委員會一次會議的資料，經調查後而作出；又稱，文翠珊對韋廉信繼續履行國防大臣職務的能力已失去信心。<br />\n<br />\n早前有外媒引述消息指出，英國政府將容許華為有限度參與當地5G基礎建設。英國文化、媒體和體育大臣衞俊明(Jeremy Wright)其後表示，將徹查國家安全委員會洩密事件，不排除對相關人士作出刑事檢控。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府仍未正式決定是否容許華為參建當地5G，首相府表示，將於今年春季末作出相關決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2127070/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A3%E9%9F%8B%E5%BB%89%E4%BF%A1%E9%81%AD%E6%92%A4%E8%81%B7+%E6%B6%89%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%B4%A9%E5%AF%86%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2127070%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2587%25A3%25E9%259F%258B%25E5%25BB%2589%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2592%25A4%25E8%2581%25B7%2B%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B4%25A9%25E5%25AF%2586%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu1CKRJWvDXkpEFRbHtszOvM%3D&h=4dd22d09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2127070/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A3%E9%9F%8B%E5%BB%89%E4%BF%A1%E9%81%AD%E6%92%A4%E8%81%B7+%E6%B6%89%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%B4%A9%E5%AF%86%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a>"},{"pid":"a4428ea30beda343d5d3f9d866ca40350c4d9769","tid":1135018,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}